            "title": "Phala Network rebrands as phala.com, a leader in privacy-preserving AI infrastructure. Founded in 2019, it launched the world's largest TEE network.",
            "id": "41dd586a-1c78-489e-af04-a7c4e74b662c",
            "description": "In San Francisco, Hashforest Technology shared news that Phala Network has changed its name to phala.com, symbolizing its transition from a Web3 project to a global confidential AI infrastructure firm. Established in 2019 by Marvin Tong and Hang Yin, Phala introduced the largest decentralized Trusted Execution Environment (TEE) network globally, initiating privacy-focused computation for blockchain networks. After enrolling in the NVIDIA Inception Program in 2025, Phala expanded its operations.",
